(580, 713, 54, 1, 0, '1551337217', '.', 'The framework of modified POMAC (M-POMAC) for efficient deallocation of the resources for benefiting various other users. The Hybrid Bat algorithm inspired by Tabu search is employed in this M-POMAC method to offer the design of decentralized mechanism for self-organizing the decisions related to offloading applications. The proposed self-organizing scheme enables to give the autonomous status for the system of mobile cloud computing thus helping for easing the complexity of the cloud management method.\r\n\r\nImplementation can be done using Java', '', '1551415163'),
(581, 712, 54, 1, 0, '1551337225', '.', 'For improvement in the segmentation process of medical image analysis. In this work, deep learning-based approach is proposed for brain tumor image segmentation. The proposed method includes the concept of Stationary Wavelet Transform (SWT) and new Growing Convolution Neural Network (GCNN). The significant objective of this work is to enhance the accuracy of the conventional system', '', '1551438233'),
