(611, 750, 54, 1, 0, '1552903018', '.', 'A LSTM network performs wells on classification and has potential to perform well on predictions of the outcome of sports.The more information the networks are fed about a match, i.e. the longer an ongoing match is played, the better the network performance\r\non predicting the outcome. This is no surprise since more information should lead to better predictions. However, the increased prediction accuracy over minutes played in a\r\nmatch indicates that the network is able to learn about and also with the LSTM we can incorporate hybrid machine learning techniques.', '', '1552974790'),
(612, 749, 31, 1, 0, '1552903170', '.', 'As per the comments from the reviewer, it is clear that the complete techniques/algorithms used needs to be changed. The comment states that new/ advanced algorithms like CNN has to be used for getting better results and comparative study needs to be done more elaborately . So implementation needs to be done with these algorithms and  modification needs to be done as per the same', '', '1554199777'),
