(630, 773, 54, 1, 0, '1554119487', '.', 'Possible Suggetion: To suggest enhanced hybrid epidemic routing algorithm. The algorithm avoids the unnecessary flooding of packets to the connection lines which have higher probability of dropping the packet. Packets were transmitted to intermediate node, only if it fulfills all the constraints mentioned here. These constraints like available buffer space and battery life ensured successful transmission of packets to their respective destinations. This resulted in a significant decrease in the overhead ratio and the traffic in the network and an increase in the message delivery probability, since packets were delivered to the intermediate nodes which have less chances of dropping them.', '', '1554191908'),
