(634, 778, 54, 1, 0, '1554262347', '.', 'Possible suggestion: While the implementation of the controller is achieved in a completely distributed fashion, the offline design of the state-feedback matrix is still centralized. The computational complexity of this centralized design may increase as the size of the power system increases. We suggest to extend this centralized design to a more distributed and computationally tractable approach and will further address the convergence properties of the proposed Reinforcement learning (RL) algorithm and extend this centralized learning method to distributed and multi-agent implementations.\r\n\r\n', '', '1554293920'),
(635, 777, 54, 1, 0, '1554262353', '.', 'Possible Suggestion: To enhance the robustness of watermarked image while considering the trade-off between transparency and robustness, a hybrid digital watermarking scheme based on DCT was proposed. Aiming at reducing the limitations, more work shall be considered, such as to relate the adaptive genetic operators to the fitness function value and ensure the convergence of the genetic algorithm; or to introduce other machine learning methods, such as neural network, to automatically calculate the embedding intensity; or to replace DCT with DWT, for the reason that DWT has the advantages of good spatial frequency characteristics and multiresolution representation and DWT has strong ability to resist noise and compression.\r\n', '', '1554295142'),
