(645, 792, 54, 1, 0, '1554785211', '.', 'Possible Suggestion: A novel SAR image retrieval approach, which includes database making, prior\r\ncategorization and similar matching. Five SAR images were\r\nused to make DB by overlapped parting. Then texture feature\r\nwere extracted using statistics of Haar wavelet coefficients,\r\nand classed images using GMM classifier. The Mean and\r\nVariance of image were applied to segmentation, then we use\r\nthem to compute the integrated region matching (IRM) distance. The evaluation of\r\napproach is query time and precision. From the experiments,\r\nour method is effectively suited to our DB. it is also a proof\r\nof feasibility of proposed approach in SAR image retrieval. ', '', '1554803462');
